rence" id="cite_ref-3"><a href="#cite_note-3">[3]</a></sup></p></p><a href=http://en.wikipedia.org/?curid=42718808 class=card-link>Link to Wikipedia Article</a></div></div><div class="card margin10"><div class=card-body><h5 class=card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted>Pulitzer Prize?</h5><p class=card-text>Yes</p></div></div><div class="card margin10"><div class=card-body><h5 class=card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted>After his family died, he threatened to kill himself. So the police took his guns.</h5><p class=card-text>A road that leads to John McGuire&#39;s home in Lisbon, Conn. (Bryan Anselm/For The Washington Post)
 
